WebSocket - WebSocket is a computer commnunication protocol,providing full-duplex (dono side A-> B or B->A) commnunication channels over a single TCP connection.

Socket.io  -- Real time applications like chatting app.

Socket.io is a JavaScript library for real-time, bi-directional communication between web clients and servers. 

---->>      npm i socket.io
---->>      const io = require('socket.io')(http);  //http is the server object 

--> Sabse pahle http server create karenge 
 const http = require('http');
const server = http.createServer(app); // ye server listen krega port ko

--> ab socket.io ko reuire krenge 
const io = require('socket.io')(server); // ye socket.io ko server se connect krega




 